{"parse":{"title":"Ultimate Healing","pageid":1923,"redirects":[{"from":"Exura Vita","to":"Ultimate Healing"}],"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><p><i>This article is about the <b>Ultimate Healing</b> <a href=\"/wiki/Instant_Spells\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Instant Spells\">instant spell</a>. For the rune, see <a href=\"/wiki/Ultimate_Healing_Rune\" title=\"Ultimate Healing Rune\">Ultimate Healing Rune</a>.</i>\n</p>\n<div class=\"twbox\">\n<aside role=\"region\" class=\"portable-infobox pi-background pi-border-color pi-theme-twbox pi-layout-default\">\n<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-item-spacing pi-title pi-secondary-background\" data-source=\"name\">Ultimate Healing</h2>\n\n<figure class=\"pi-item pi-image\">\n\t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/tibia/images/3/31/Ultimate_Healing.gif/revision/latest?cb=20110109121520&amp;path-prefix=en\" class=\"image image-thumbnail\" title=\"Ultimate Healing\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/tibia/images/3/31/Ultimate_Healing.gif/revision/latest?cb=20110109121520&amp;path-prefix=en\" srcset=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/tibia/images/3/31/Ultimate_Healing.gif/revision/latest?cb=20110109121520&amp;path-prefix=en 1x, https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/tibia/images/3/31/Ultimate_Healing.gif/revision/latest?cb=20110109121520&amp;path-prefix=en 2x\" class=\"pi-image-thumbnail\" data-relevant=\"1\" alt=\"Ultimate Healing\" width=\"38\" height=\"38\" data-image-key=\"Ultimate_Healing.gif\" data-image-name=\"Ultimate Healing.gif\" />\n\t\t\n\t</a>\n\t\n</figure>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Usage Properties</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"words\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Words</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><span class=\"tibiatext tibiayellow\">exura vita</span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"mana\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Mana</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">160</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"subclass\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Group</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><span class=\"no-pseudoelements-container\"><span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Healing_Spells\" title=\"Healing Spells\"><img alt=\"Healing Spells\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/tibia/images/e/ef/Healing_Cooldown.png/revision/latest?cb=20210518022831&amp;path-prefix=en\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Healing Cooldown.png\" data-image-key=\"Healing_Cooldown.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" /></a></span></span>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Healing_Spells\" title=\"Healing Spells\">Healing</a>&#160;(1 sec CD)</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"cooldown\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Individual Cooldown</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">1 second</div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Requirement Properties</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"voc\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Vocation</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Druid\" title=\"Druid\">Druid</a><br /><a href=\"/wiki/Sorcerer\" title=\"Sorcerer\">Sorcerer</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"premium\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Premium</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><span class=\"no-cross\" title=\"No\">&#10007;</span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"promotion\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Promotion</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><span class=\"no-cross\" title=\"No\">&#10007;</span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"levelrequired\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Level</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">30</div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Other Properties</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"basepower\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Base Power</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">250</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"implemented\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Version</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Unknown.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"status\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Status</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Active</div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<nav class=\"pi-navigation pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-font\"><p>\t    See also: <a href=\"/wiki/Spells\" title=\"Spells\">Spells</a>\t    <span class=\"explained\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:Infobox_Spell#Usage\" title=\"Template:Infobox Spell\">Help</a></span></p></nav>\n</aside>\n\n <div style=\"clear:left;\"></div>\n <div id=\"twbox-effect\">\n  <h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Effect\">Effect</span></h3>\n<p>Restores a large amount of <a href=\"/wiki/HP\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"HP\">health</a> and cures <a href=\"/wiki/Paralysis\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Paralysis\">paralysis</a>.\n</p>\n </div>\n <div id=\"twbox-notes\">\n  <h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span></h3>\n<div class=\"webdesc\">\n    <blockquote class=\"webdesc-text\"><p>This spell was invented by one of the very first druids, and to this day it represents one of the ultimate achievements in salutary magic. By using it a skilled spell caster can heal the worst of injuries in the blink of an eye, instantly recovering even if he was mortally wounded just seconds ago. Eager to share their knowledge and to bring good into the world, the druids gave this spell to the sorcerers, but they quickly started to bitterly regret this step, for the improved methods of self-healing only led many to be even more careless with their own lives and with those of others. Thus, while the spell saved countless lives over the centuries, it paradoxically also caused the loss of many others. Nonetheless, it is a crucial spell that should not miss in any druid's or sorcerer's spellbook.</p></blockquote>\n\t<div class=\"webdesc-from\" style=\"float: right; margin: 0 2em 0 0;\">&#8212;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tibia.com/library/?subtopic=spells&amp;spell=ultimatehealing\">Tibia Library</a></div>\n\t<div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n  </div>\n  <div id=\"spell-animation\"><table class=\"scene&#95;table canvas\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"padding:32px;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>\n\t<div class=\"tile\">\n\t<div class=\"effect\"></div>\n\t<div class=\"caster-east\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/tibia/images/9/93/Mage_Outfit_Male_White.gif/revision/latest?cb=20171019130455&amp;path-prefix=en\" alt=\"latest?cb=20171019130455&amp;path-prefix=en\" /></div>\n\t<div class=\"effect\"><img src=\"https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/Special:Redirect/file/Blue_Sparkles_Effect.gif\" alt=\"Blue_Sparkles_Effect.gif\" /></div>\n\t<div class=\"effect no&#95;effect\"><img src=\"https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/Special:Redirect/file/Blue_Sparkles_Effect.gif\" alt=\"Blue_Sparkles_Effect.gif\" /></div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</tr></tbody></table></div>\n </div>\n<div id=\"spell-history\" class=\"history-section\">\n  <h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h3>\n<ul><li>Since the <a href=\"/wiki/Winter_Update_2007\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Winter Update 2007\">Winter Update 2007</a>, when <a href=\"/wiki/Holy_Damage\" title=\"Holy Damage\">holy</a> spells were introduced, Ultimate Healing became useless for <a href=\"/wiki/Paladin\" title=\"Paladin\">paladins</a>, as <a href=\"/wiki/Divine_Healing\" title=\"Divine Healing\">Divine Healing</a> restores significantly more health while costing only 50 mana more. For that reason, it was eventually made available only for mages.</li></ul>\n </div>\n <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n <div class=\"navigation\">\n <h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Related_Spells\">Related Spells</span></h3>\n<div class=\"navigation-body\">\n<h4><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Healing_Spells\">Healing Spells</span></h4>\n<div class=\"navigation-list-wrapper\"><ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Bruise_Bane\" title=\"Bruise Bane\">Bruise Bane</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Cure_Bleeding\" title=\"Cure Bleeding\">Cure Bleeding</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Cure_Burning\" title=\"Cure Burning\">Cure Burning</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Cure_Curse\" title=\"Cure Curse\">Cure Curse</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Cure_Electrification\" title=\"Cure Electrification\">Cure Electrification</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Cure_Poison\" title=\"Cure Poison\">Cure Poison</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Divine_Healing\" title=\"Divine Healing\">Divine Healing</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Fair_Wound_Cleansing\" title=\"Fair Wound Cleansing\">Fair Wound Cleansing</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Gift_of_Life\" title=\"Gift of Life\">Gift of Life</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Heal_Friend\" title=\"Heal Friend\">Heal Friend</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Intense_Healing\" title=\"Intense Healing\">Intense Healing</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Intense_Recovery\" title=\"Intense Recovery\">Intense Recovery</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Intense_Wound_Cleansing\" title=\"Intense Wound Cleansing\">Intense Wound Cleansing</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Light_Healing\" title=\"Light Healing\">Light Healing</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Magic_Patch\" title=\"Magic Patch\">Magic Patch</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Mass_Healing\" title=\"Mass Healing\">Mass Healing</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Mass_Spirit_Mend\" title=\"Mass Spirit Mend\">Mass Spirit Mend</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Nature%27s_Embrace\" title=\"Nature&#39;s Embrace\">Nature&#39;s Embrace</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Recovery\" title=\"Recovery\">Recovery</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Restoration\" title=\"Restoration\">Restoration</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Restore_Balance\" title=\"Restore Balance\">Restore Balance</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Salvation\" title=\"Salvation\">Salvation</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Spirit_Mend\" title=\"Spirit Mend\">Spirit Mend</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Wound_Cleansing\" title=\"Wound Cleansing\">Wound Cleansing</a></li></ul></div>\n </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260718003051\nCache expiry: 3600\nReduced expiry: true\nComplications: [no\u2010toc]\nCPU time usage: 0.075 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.107 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 976/1000000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 19003/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 5180/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 16/100\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 28/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.004/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 672020/104857600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   86.429      1 Template:Infobox_Spell\n100.00%   86.429      1 -total